Invisible Habitudes《看不见的归属》
.
As part of their “Moving through Covid-19” 2020 fundraising efforts to help support the company in these difficult times, T.H.E Dance Company have released their archival footage and materials for Invisible Habitudes《看不见的归属》 for a limited time! .
The video will be available for viewing from 7 May 2020 to 20 May 2020:
https://www.apart.sg/featured-season-5/the-invisible-habitudes
.
